remixlab.proscene

Class KeyboardShortcut

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.proscene.KeyboardShortcut

  • public final class KeyboardShortcut
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents keyboard shortcuts.

    Keyboard shortcuts can be of one out of three forms: 1. Characters (e.g., 'a'); 2. Virtual keys (e.g., right arrow key); or, 3. Key combinations (e.g., 'a' + CTRL key).
